  li Download und Installation des Virtualbox Extension Packs (<a href="http://download.virtualbox.org/virtualbox/4.3.32/Oracle_VM_VirtualBox_Extension_Pack-4.3.32-103443.vbox-extpack">link</a>)
  li Download des Virtualbox Images (<a href="http://files.htw-webtech.com/htw-webtech-ws-2015.ova">link</a>)

